# Signal Proposal: Multi-Sig Signer Nomination & Election
## Comprehensive Technical Specification

---

## Executive Summary

This proposal introduces a three-phase, transparent process for nominating and electing Multi-Sig wallet signers, incorporating both traditional governance mechanisms and experimental on-chain components. The goal is to accelerate AavegotchiDAO's measured transition to full on-chain governance while maintaining security and community involvement.

---

