## Appendices

### Appendix A: Glossary

- **diamondCut():** Smart contract function that allows protocol upgrades
- **Multi-Sig:** Multi-signature wallet requiring multiple approvals
- **Signal Proposal:** Off-chain vote to gauge community support
- **Core Proposal:** On-chain vote with binding execution
- **Quorum:** Minimum voting power required for valid decision
- **ValuePoints:** Assessment currency for candidate evaluation

### Appendix B: Example Timeline

```
Day 1-3 (72h):   Phase I.A - Nominations open
Day 4-6 (72h):   Phase I.B - Role definition & assessments
Day 7-13 (7d):   Phase II - Signal Proposal on Snapshot
Day 14-21 (7d):  Phase III - Core Proposal on-chain
Day 22-28:       Results & Signer Transition
Feb 28:          New signers officially begin term
```

